Axon - Wordnik & Wikipedia Firefox add-on

Axon provides access to the Wordnik dictionary and all Wikipedia
articles in every language. Double-clicking on a word opens the
Wordnik dictionary definition in a speech bubble.
If the word can not be found Axon continues on Wikipedia.


